      "content": "It is very important that you do **not** change your warfarin dosage on your own. Warfarin dosage needs to be carefully managed by your healthcare provider based on regular blood tests called INR checks. Please schedule an appointment with your doctor or pharmacist to discuss your concerns about the dose. They can safely monitor your blood levels and determine if a reduction is appropriate for your specific needs.",
